Title: selection of host dropdowns now possible with arrow keys
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1574177702
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0i1

The selection of autocomplete host dropdown fields is now possible by using the up and down arrow keys.
These dropdown field can for example be found in every rule in the 'Explicit hosts' section.
